data.description: Step into charm with this 2-story gem! Main floor master, cozy fireplace in the living room and a new kitchen flaunting shiplap backsplash. Enjoy a spacious dining area with original pocket doors and an abundance of natural light. Upstairs has 3 large bedrooms with tall ceilings and 2.5 bathrooms make mornings a breeze. The large yard, privacy fence. and patio are perfect for entertaining. Plus a heated 2-car garage on a corner lot completes this picture-perfect home!
